# Antigravity Rules - Coding Standards

## Language & Naming
- **Code Language:** All code, variables, function names, and comments MUST be in English.
- **Naming Convention:** - Variables/Functions: `camelCase`
    - Components/Classes: `PascalCase`
    - Constants: `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE`
    - Files: `kebab-case` or match component name.

## Database Schema (English)
- Tables: `products`, `sync_queue`, `categories`, `users`.
- Fields: `id`, `uuid`, `name`, `description`, `price`, `quantity`, `is_synced`, `created_at`.